    'Mt 13:11': 'And he, answering, said to them, "Because to you it has been given to know the mysteries of the kingdom of the heavens, but to those it has not been given.',
    'Mt 13:12': 'For whoever has, [more] will be given to him and he will have abundance; but whoever does not have, even what he has will be taken from him.',
