    'Mt 26:54': 'How then would the scriptures be fulfilled, that thus it must happen?',
    'Mt 26:56': 'But this whole [thing] has happened in order that the scriptures of the prophets might be fulfilled. Then all the disciples, leaving him, fled.',
    'Mt 27:22': 'Pilate says to them, "What therefore shall I do [with] Jesus, the one called Christ?" They all say, "Let him be crucified."',
